{"tid":1857414,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[大陸網民嬲嬲豬]武漢紅十字會又被曝光","createTime":"2020-02-02T07:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T08:06:55.000Z","uid":304366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"44660488fd35bd83c598892fdd7a0063c9457df4","tid":1857414,"uid":304366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T07:29:38.000Z","msg":"咁話説就係大陸人發現所有用順豐速遞等方法寄過去嘅物資，都會唔知點解統一比曬紅十，又比人話收咗再賣出去收錢。<br />\n<br />\n然後明明比間武漢仁愛醫院1.6萬個口罩，出到嚟條數唔啱，改做1.8萬個。<br />\n<br />\n而更加重要嘅係，嗰間醫院係專做婦產科，亦都唔係發熱門診定點醫院，最需要口罩嘅協和醫院反而得個3000個口罩。<br />\n<br />\n之後又澄清話啲口罩唔係n95，協和直接有人去拎口罩又唔比人。<br />\n<br />\n然後而家央視直播紅十倉庫想幫佢洗底，又比個保安趕走左，依家瀨晒嘢，但我肯定疫情一過就冇人會記得，就好似當年郭美美咁樣。<br />\n<br />\n大陸人就好嬲嬲，但嬲完仲要比人刪帖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28ngFGX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28ngFGX.png&h=28f9cf6a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R2ZritD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR2ZritD.png&h=d40bc3b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fjVNNmZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfjVNNmZ.png&h=d651b7ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sB4buAk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsB4buAk.png&h=2863c94f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢哋仲整合唒紅十一直以來嘅衰嘢：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xdyGRO9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxdyGRO9.jpg&h=221acc9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有陳秋實明顯係維穩工具啦，佢嘅信用評分扣到仲可以搭火車咩？講啲大家都知嘅嘢，鬧一鬧下共產黨，等你以為係自己人。然之後就將大陸想俾你睇到嘅嘢出嚟：而家醫院淨係物資唔夠啊，但其實都好守秩序。<br />\n<br />\n乜撚嘢火神山呀2000個床位，你一日都「新增」咗依個數啦。屌，見到啲武漢人到其他地方，比人封晒啲門口唔俾人出，好撚慘。成單嘢瞞報到同切爾諾貝爾一鬼樣，而家咪冚家剷囉。<br />\n<br />\n比大家睇下真係講真話嘅人嘅下場：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vbfJ5cD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvbfJ5cD.png&h=e14a9ba9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a1eb9f2a7f44a9cbffb1f7c3bd35f8107c517d3","tid":1857414,"uid":38164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T07:49:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">越描越黑<br />\n越揭越臭<br />\n腐敗</span>"},{"pid":"7e28de9f603dc22f31dde1f0ba6b3c54a880166a","tid":1857414,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T07:54:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200202&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60551035\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200202%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60551035&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9PGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=ddfeb894\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200202%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60551035&h=c47dee0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200202&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60551035</a><br />\n<br />\n廣東人衝落緊嚟"},{"pid":"b312b1a04b6be5992dbdb051bc744b741257bf55","tid":1857414,"uid":101307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:06:55.000Z","msg":"香港嗰間都係咁啦"}]}